    "description": {
      "zh": "战斗兴奋剂。由 TerraGroup 实验室开发，编号为P22。当身体组织暴露在外时，它可促使内部肌肉包含被动，使身体组织受到较少的损伤。它被用来在战斗前扩展身体的能力。授权给特种部队士兵使用，有副作用。",
      "en": "A combat stimulant. Developed by TerraGroup Labs, marked as P22. It allows the tissues of the body to receive less damage when physically exposed due to passive inclusion in the work of internal muscles. It is used to expand the body's abilities before a fight. Authorized for use by special forces soldiers. Has side effects."
    },
